@startuml
[*] --> CreateAccount: The system shall allow a user to create an account.
CreateAccount --> Login: The system shall enable a user to watch videos after they have created an account.
Login --> WatchVideo: The system shall permit a user to upload videos.
WatchVideo --> SaveVideo: The system shall allow a user to save videos in their likes list during video viewing.
SaveVideo --> ViewSavedVideos: The system shall enable a user to view their saved videos from the likes list.
ViewSavedVideos --> DiscussionOption: The system shall allow a user to enter the discussion option.
@enduml
